snippet.title: Nation Pays Last Respects To Nayak S K Vidyarthi And Sunil Kumar From Bihar Martyred In Uri Attacks

localized.description:
The nation is paying last respects to Nayak S K Vidyarthi and Sunil Kumar from Bihar for their ultimate sacrifice for the nation in the Uri Attacks.
